      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in exceptional, mint condition and represents a rare find in the used car market. The car shows virtually no signs of wear, with a flawless exterior finish free of scratches, dents, or paint fade. The interior is immaculate, with pristine upholstery, fully functional controls, and no odors or staining of any kind. Mechanically, the vehicle performs at the highest level, with all systems operating as intended and no known issues to disclose. This is the kind of used car that feels nearly indistinguishable from new, and it has been exceptionally well maintained throughout its life. A buyer can expect a turnkey experience with minimal to no immediate maintenance needs.",
